Story about wedding planners, how these two fall in love while starting  a new wedding planning service , Shaadi Mubarak. The songs are to die for , Ainya Ainya, you will love the visuals of this movie, colors sound.  I met my fiancee while this movie was being shot at the JW Mariott.  Buy this
